::Havoc/Zardus::

Havoc nods, entering the bridge of the Iron Fist and walking up to 
FZ. Repressor was following behind him near Demolition.

"Any orders, sir?" he asks him. FZ turns around, standing up.

"Yes. Something just happened at the Destron base, but some bots are 
still there. Can you go to them and see if they need assistance?"

Havoc nods. "We'll be there in a flash, sir."

He turns and walks off toward the exit of the Iron Fist, motioning 
for the others to follow.
